#import "/formatting.typ": *
#import "/shared-data.typ": *

#recipe(title: "Refried Beans")[
  - Dried beans
  - 1 tomato, blended
  - Salt, to taste#Footnotes.bean-seasoning
  - Cumin, 1 pinch
  - Butter, 2 tbsp.

  *Yields multiple bowls.*
][
  + RINSE beans in cold running water.
  + SOAK overnight. #Footnotes.bean-stinking #Footnotes.bean-expansion #pause[12-24 hr.]
  + STRAIN and return to rice cooker.
  + ADD tomato, dry seasonings.
  + ADD water to fill line.
  + BOIL, checking water level occasionally. #pause[up to 2 hr., 15-30 min. intervals]
  + STRAIN beans into food processor, and blend. Keep leftover water; it is tasty.
  + FRY beans with butter.
  + SERVE fresh, refrigerate for 1-2 weeks, or freeze until needed.
]


== Trivia

@R_bean-soup-rice-cooker[Bean Soup] was derived from this recipe.
